step.info:
Make sure you follow these rules:

The file must be well-formed.

The code for each script element must be included in an XML
              comment.

The start and end tags for the XML comment must be on a separate line.
          The content of the XML file should look like
          this:<div id="twitter">
  <a href="https://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button">Tweet</a>
  <script>
